txt.en: Nâmi has asked you to travel to the cave in Dul Râkh and thin the number of scorpions in the area.
Defeat scorpions inside the cave at Dul Râkh for Nâmi at the Dumûri camp in Urash Dâr.
Defeat scorpions in Dul Râkh cave ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Return to Nâmi in Urash Dâr and let her know you have thinned the number of scorpions in Dul Râkh.
Defeated scorpions in Dul Râkh cave ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'Greetings, [placeholder].

'I gather that you have returned from Dul Râkh successful in your task. I thank you for your help in this fight.

'The Anâkhi and their beasts will be less of a threat for now.'
Nâmi has asked you thin out the number of scorpions in Dul Râkh to the west.

'[placeholder], I am glad to see you here. We here have been battling with the Anâkhi in their cave, Dul Râkh, nearby.\n\n'I ask that you help us to turn the tide as we are needed in many places since Utug-bûr was opened. If you can, go to Dul Râkh and find their cave. Inside you must cleanse it of these vicious scorpions that the Anâkhi worship.'
